Class ConsumptionDB

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.arch.persistence.room.RoomDatabase
      • edu.cnm.deepdive.green_print.model.ConsumptionDB

  • public abstract class ConsumptionDB
extends android.arch.persistence.room.RoomDatabase
    Uses a singleton pattern to implement a single app-wide connection by defining the local database assembled by its entities and converters. Asserts methods to obtain data access objects (DAOs) for the database entities.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Kevin Simms & Deep Dive Coding Java + Android Bootcamp cohort 6
